snippet.description:
Mario Maker Speed Run FAIL! ►► http://bit.ly/1NrjhoU
Subscribing to GLive? No Contest! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 

Welcome to the second episode in our Retro Sabotage series! Today we played Megaman X and tried to beat it using YOUR sabotages! Can we play while wearing oven mitts? While hanging upside down? While stuffing marshmallows in my face? Can Stephanie even beat the tutorial level?! Watch and find out.

Special Thanks to NateWantsToBattle for Joining us! ►► https://www.youtube.com/user/NateWantsToBattle

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
